{"serial": "09016", "department_serial": 3, "code": "GS3056", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Local knowledge ans society", "ch": "地方知識與社會"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Fu, Bao-Yu"], "ch": ["傅寶玉"]}, "credits": 2, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["6", "7"]}, "loc": {"building": "O", "room": "209"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 120, "department": {"ch": "通識教育中心", "en": "General Education Center"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 10, "selected": 64, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程將引導學生認識“地方“的途徑，講解有關地方的知識，地方與權力的關連，並從生命的經驗出發，思考人與地方如何產生情感聯繫，如何認同、記憶、想像地方，又如何排斥某些元素進入「我們的」地方，並思索「地方特色」是否因全球化而消失。\n\n本課程將帶領 同學由探索地方出發，找尋自我經驗的意義與知識關懷的框架，進而轉化成為社會學習與行動力量。除講解與地方知識相關的議題與案例分享外， 並透過記錄影片觀賞與講評做為輔助，進一步闡釋基本概念，培養學生獨立思考與批判關懷能力 。", "en": "“Under the influence of globalization, people are getting further away from locality, and more disconnected from land. However, local identity and locality have not disappeared. Local society, being a source of community experience, persists and reappears in another way. It tries to reinvigorate with the unique local culture and community movement in the face of globalization. In a global era, localization has become a concern of the sustainable development  of all countries. How to create a distinctive local society and culture has become the fundamental consensus of “Think Globally Act Locally”. This course will start with exploration of locality and place, and help students to find the meaning of self-experience and the frame of local knowledge, which hopefully will develop into the power of social learning and action.“"}, "outline": {"ch": "“1. 導言\n2. 什麼是地方?\n3. 什麼是地方的人?\n4. 水利與地方\n5. 家與家屋的想像\n6. 地方的宗教與儀式\n7. 地景與權力\n7. 空間聚落與地景\n8. 文學地景：書寫與地方\n9. 電影、電視與音樂中的地方想像\n10. 田野中的地方與地方中的田野\n11. 網路與地方塑造\n12. 地方記憶與社群\n13. 商品與消費的地方\n14. 地方與全球化\n15. 地方社會個案與地方創生(一)\n16. 地方社會個案與地方創生(二)\n17  作為地方行動者\n18  期末報告“", "en": "“This course is composed of lectures on various issues of local knowledge, and some discussions about the basic concepts through viewing short films. The students will be organized into groups, and each group should complete filming a ““local field work““ on a chosen subject and make a class report.\n1.Introduction 2. What Is local knowledge?  3 What is locality? 4.Imagination about the house and home.5. Landscape and power 6. Rural settlements and water conservancy 7. Literary landscape: writing and geography 8. Imagination of locality  in movies, TV and music 9.  What is field work? And how to do field work. 10. Religion and ritual in the local society 11. Local memory and community 12. The place, goods and consumption 13. Visible and invisible city 14. Locality and Globalization 15. Case study on local society and field investigation(I )16. Case study on local society and field investigation(II) 17. As a local actor 18. Summary"}, "textbook": {"ch": "“1.Mike Crang著 王志弘等譯， 《文化地理學》 \n2.Clifford Geertz著，楊德睿譯， 《地方知識》\n3. Tim Cresswel著，徐苔玲等譯，l地方：記憶、想像與認同。", "en": "Tim Cresswell, Place: a short introduction   Wiley, 2004.\nClifford Geertz.  Local Knowledge: further essays in interpretive anthropology  New York: Basic Books, c1983.“"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "60%", "en": "60%"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討\n\n\n其他", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar", "", "", "Others"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "學生將進行分組討論與期末田野調查記錄。\n\n出席與討論 20％ (出席及參與課堂討論與提問)\n平時作業或期中考試 40％ (課堂學習單) \n期末分組報告 40％ (自訂與地方議題有關的題目完成分組報告。(影像拍攝或書面方式擇一呈現)", "en": "Homework 40％ \nTeamwork reports 40％   Fieldwork Report by grouping work.\nClass discussion and attendance 20％“"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "請先跟教師預約", "en": "Appointment"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "社會思潮與現象領域", "en": "社會思潮與現象領域"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "邏輯與創新", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}